      "body" : "@laanwj: I recently played around with max QR size/bytes, black/white (inverted) and the white-space-border. I could not find any specification about the \"quite zone\" (white border), but I guess \"one square width\" as min border size should be more as sufficient. I guess it depends on the QRCode reader implementation. But I could not read the QRCode with common readers if there where no white borders.",
